WEBVTT

00:01:56.941 --> 00:02:00.584
I'm inviting myself inside the minds
of some truly unusual people,

00:02:00.608 --> 00:02:03.766
because they've mastered something
I wish everyone knew about work.

00:02:04.188 --> 00:02:06.276
Today: career callings,

00:02:06.300 --> 00:02:10.204
and why following your passion could be
some of the worst advice you ever get.

00:02:10.616 --> 00:02:13.823
(Music)

00:02:14.846 --> 00:02:18.025
Thanks to JPMorgan Chase
for sponsoring this episode.

00:02:18.049 --> 00:02:22.660
(Music)

00:02:22.974 --> 00:02:25.494
Alright, I understand why
"follow your passion"

00:02:25.518 --> 00:02:27.518
is such popular career advice.

00:02:27.919 --> 00:02:31.276
Chances are you spend the majority
of your waking hours at work.